{"tid":1571053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「國際戰線」穿越10000公里於西班牙巴塞魯營舉起「光復香港」旗幟","createTime":"2019-09-15T10:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:28:52.000Z","uid":80234,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3217d83bbb426bee930229d83a305976ea0038","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"尋晚去巴塞現場睇波 （21:00 開波）<br />\n<br />\n（利申曼迷，但球會係喜好，黑白是良知）<br />\n<br />\n平時睇 live stream 見人舉國旗舉橫額就舉得多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解自己入場睇唔試下舉呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n舉完直播影到又可以幫香港宣傳下，又可以激勵下大家士氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDy0eGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDy0eGx.png&h=dc792f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後因爲香港 research 一輪到唔知點邊到抖直接有旗埋<br />\n<br />\n就係巴塞展開左搵旗之旅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （到達巴塞已經深夜）<br />\n<br />\n自己認知有塊布有顏料就得<br />\n<br />\n好彩巴塞都好多賣美術用品地方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GoHDLQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoHDLQF.png&h=7b773c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一間顏料舖 （16:00）<br />\n<br />\n買左啲 textile 用顏料同畫筆<br />\n<br />\n最後實測上唔到色<br />\n<br />\n返到hostel 要行衝返去買過 Van Gogh 油畫 style 顏料先上到色<br />\n<br />\n入面冇布賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但展長知識了有啲100% cotton 嘅紙都好近磅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxxTzLt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxxTzLt.png&h=bdeeed83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行過第二間舖，成間都係紙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （16:30）<br />\n<br />\n有啲質地跟加似布 rayon 做tim<br />\n<br />\n不過作為連登仔，未到最後一刻都唔會退而求其次<br />\n<br />\n係隔離西裝 post  cd rom 禁耐令我知道呢個世界係有地方賣布 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為何巴塞隆那沒有深水埗？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但搵到間幾正常嘅布舖就買左1 m黑布 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （17:00）<br />\n<br />\n仲同老闆日本呀姨傾左陣香港嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">（呢個旅程好多人有關心香港點，有人想知再講）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Riuns7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRiuns7s.png&h=ac9a2d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到hostel 就開工啦 （17:15）<br />\n<br />\n好在陽台有位做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tTbMUOF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtTbMUOF.png&h=7a8231b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面樓仲有加泰人掛黃絲抗議西班牙政府打壓加泰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1KKGuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1KKGuF.png&h=04b832cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（周街都有其實，有人想知再post圖，覺得香港可以借鏡，如果周街都掛光復香港旗會營造到好嘅氛圍）<br />\n<br />\n製作中，好遺憾自己唔識書法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDhDLWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDhDLWS.png&h=5fc57f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有當自己畫家 x 書法家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後趕及係魯營舉起「光復香港」旗 （21:00）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcOWxCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcOWxCV.png&h=ea63d6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資源緊拙我google translate 同上網睇新聞 liberate 香港西班牙文點譯咋<br />\n<br />\n中場休息先上到禁前影咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （21:45）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AidC1xu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAidC1xu.png&h=31f74551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉旗影相時，有日韓球迷似係認得句slogan <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有中國球迷眼超超<br />\n<br />\n題外話，時間緊迫，啲油未乾架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKs0ZnL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKs0ZnL.png&h=8b191ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nReview:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7J5aB9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7J5aB9A.png&h=81d0ceb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>買位方面</ins><br />\n<br />\n如果大家想舉旗唔好揀呢個區域，因為係簷蓬底，live影唔到好多，唔近唔遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買高啲同後備席對面個 stand 係最佳位置，全場 live影住，我坐嗰邊一家舉足全場<br />\n<br />\n==========================<br />\n<br />\n打完篇文我出門做返個普通遊客啦<br />\n<br />\n去吃喝玩樂同關注香港係冇抵觸<br />\n<br />\n都一樣可以用你方法為光復香港出一份力，哪怕只係舉個旗（同埋唔怕醜咁整旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），貼張光復香港  sticker 係 gip, 或者係同旅途中預到嘅人分享香港真實情況<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\nps. 有冇人之後有地方去想舉旗又懶得整又搵唔到，唔嫌棄可以pass枝旗俾你<br />\n<br />\n利申：打算係香港 arrival 時再舉"},{"pid":"9769ba7060e92babe6d0c0dd166ca201ea0ad127","tid":1571053,"uid":279922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5a7b740781cd20f6e0ea050da2c8c0a83d235b27","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jW3zjr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjW3zjr8.png&h=33b201fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAverage position of attacking centre back Pique<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實兩隊攻嗰時中堅都壓過左人半場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBx0Zs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBx0Zs9.png&h=944a1369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 attacking goalkeeper 紐亞接班人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到香港我會入場睇香港隊啦"},{"pid":"6269c6aa62d741dbbd832691b9f43b22e95ec0b8","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"巴都入五球呀<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubjKHuX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubjKHuX.png&h=aed63d84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c56663ab2795f02fbb07534cb0351bcadb8ddf3","tid":1571053,"uid":294831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾啲中國佬見到好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf87cdfdb94bf67a7464c62593ee4ee03df8d08","tid":1571053,"uid":8587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:47:48.000Z","msg":"黎緊都出國去中東國家，想問出境係咪應該無乜問題？<br />\n我老母係咁叫我唔好帶去，又驚呢驚路咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216f298e08e323e7c2b9811e8275a296348755c8","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf87cdfdb94bf67a7464c62593ee4ee03df8d08","tid":1571053,"uid":8587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:47:48.000Z","msg":"黎緊都出國去中東國家，想問出境係咪應該無乜問題？<br />\n我老母係咁叫我唔好帶去，又驚呢驚路咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:15:20.000Z","msg":"我都答你唔到呀<br />\n<br />\n因為我枝旗去到先整<br />\n<br />\n但機場出境我唔多覺要經海關bor<br />\n<br />\n機場保安之後就過入境處<br />\n<br />\n你帶旗都唔關呢兩家事<br />\n<br />\n我個 gip 痴左光復香港經機場入口過禁制令check point 都冇俾人截<br />\n<br />\n聽日落機唔知會點呢"},{"pid":"578ed402bc851a454f32bab0c1390292bb4b8926","tid":1571053,"uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打 係咪買返mes que un club個位最好? thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe386571b7cbca239863efd94819df80a146e9a","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"578ed402bc851a454f32bab0c1390292bb4b8926","tid":1571053,"uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打 係咪買返mes que un club個位最好? thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"你意思係 for 睇波定點？<br />\n放睇波同上鏡同多人睇到 banner 嗰個位都贏"},{"pid":"2c71ae04825bacaba2128fdd5333235aef27c599","tid":1571053,"uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe386571b7cbca239863efd94819df80a146e9a","tid":1571053,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"578ed402bc851a454f32bab0c1390292bb4b8926","tid":1571053,"uid":102994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打 係咪買返mes que un club個位最好? thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"你意思係 for 睇波定點？<br />\n放睇波同上鏡同多人睇到 banner 嗰個位都贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"係呀 不過我發現我喺barcelona既時間疤冇主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以算<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d1b467ec2479b44da1957ce575f98e35374ab7","tid":1571053,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T21:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/